node package_proxy.js create-react-app install
node package_proxy.js axios uninstall
```
These solutions provide a medium complexity CLI tool for managing packages using multiple package managers. The user can interact with the tool using command-line arguments, and the tool will forward the commands to the appropriate package manager based on the package name.

